13. Kb1 { We are not in a hurry and can improve the position of our king before proceeding with the attack on the kingside. } Nf6 
14. Ng5 $5  {[%cal Gd2e4]} { Now that Black has temporarily stopped our pawn storm (although 14.g4 was also possible), I would like to show you this interesting attacking idea that we haven't seen before. } h6 
