12. Nxe4 Qe7 
13. Qc2 {[%cal Ge4d6,Gd3h7,Gc2c6]} { With a double threat of Qc6 and Nxd6 followed by Bxh7+. Black cannot easily defend against both threats! } Bb7 ( 13...Bf4 14.g3 Bh6 15.Ne5 $14 { with an almost overwhelming initiative. } ) 
14. Nxd6 Qxd6 
15. Bxh7+ Kh8 
