2. Nf3 ( 2.Nf3 { This chapter is devoted to all the 2nd move sidelines that we haven't covered in other chapters. Specifically, we cover deviations from } 2...g6 { , } ( 2...e6 { , } ) ( 2...d5 { , and } ) ( 2...c5 { , which are by far the main options for Black. } ) ) b6 { In some cases, this can transpose to the Queen's Indian Torre chapter, but Black has some moves with independent value. } 
3. Bg5 Bb7 
