6. e3 { We continue our development as usual. } d6 { Black doesn't need to castle in this position which, as we have seen, can be quite dangerous! } 
7. Bd3 {[%mdl 32768]} Nbd7 
8. O-O { Here we can simply castle. We basically give up our attack on the h-file, but we can then control the center with e4, which was our other idea. } O-O 
