26. Nb3 c4 
27. Nd4 {[%csl Gd4]} { Now Black's position is collapsing. The knight on d4 is just a fantastic piece. } Rxg3 
28. Qxg3+ Qg6 
29. Qd6 { The knight on f6 is pinned. } Rf7 
30. Nf5 Qg5 
31. Qe6 Kf8 
32. Nd6 { Black resigned. } 1-0

